&lt;p&gt;While building on our culture of:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Doing it Right&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Doing it Safe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Doing it Well&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;u&gt;Essential Duties and Responsibilities&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Safety&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read and understand the Crescent Safety Playbook – Doing it Safe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure a safe work environment is maintained&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage in the Safety Observation process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure a preventive maintenance tasks are completed one time and correctly&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all equipment is operating safely&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all line work and machine tasks are being completed in a safe manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure a clean and organized workspace, and hold themselves to a high standard and lives the “leave work areas better than found them”.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continually seek out and remove forms of risk created by our equipment and equipment setup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;People&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical leadership and troubleshooting capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a leader in training for all other personnel at Crescent who will interact and or operate with equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recognize to ensure each person feels appreciated for the value they provide&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead people to encourage maximum performance and dedication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Productivity&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform tasks associated with setup and preventative maintenance of the equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all line setup are done correctly, safely and on time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Look for and create Continuous improvement ideas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide a first level of troubleshooting and machine diagnostic when equipment is not performing properly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be able to setup and operate any auxiliary equipment such as labelers and printers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate issues and opportunities to the site Production Leader or Supervisors&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Equipment Changeovers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Quality&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all equipment is operating in a manner that produces quality product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate any suspected quality issues to the appropriate person&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in root cause analysis on quality issues and be part of corrective action development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide consultation along with Quality leader and Ops leadership on all new builds to ensure “quality at the source” design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Customer Value&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the proper care and use of equipment – Crescent and Customer owned equipment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide real time support to customer trials, samples and visits&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Financial&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be knowledgeable of impact of equipment costs on Crescent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use equipment, support and other materials appropriately&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
