&lt;li&gt;Continually seek out and remove all forms of risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report all safety, quality, near misses, accidents, mistakes and product damages accurately and according to processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comply with all OSHA, ISO and company standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
