&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Position Summary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Crescent GE Material Handlers are responsible to perform their assigned duties in a manner which is safe, and efficient while focusing on proper handling of materials in the receiving, packing, picking, and shipping processes. The business will operate as outlined in the Crescent Way- 3 P’s:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Purpose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;People&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While building on our culture of:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Doing it Right&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Doing it Safe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Doing it Well&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Essential Duties and Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safety&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read and understand the Crescent Safety Playbook – Doing it Safe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure a work environment which is safe and maintained where our people can safely grow and develop&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continually seek out and remove all forms of risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report all safety, quality, near misses, accidents, mistakes and product damages accurately and according to processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comply with all OSHA, ISO and company standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;People&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion the Crescent Culture of Doing it Right, Doing it Safe and Doing it Well and abide by all written and understood procedures and policies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pack, sort and stacking products throughout the shift and review completed tasks for accuracy and completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicates well and respectfully with others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Committed to working with leadership&#39;s goals and requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cooperates with new ideas, actively participates in providing new ideas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible &amp;amp; adaptable to the needs of the operation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Productivity&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Works at a pace to achieve production and quality goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure and verify all receiving, picking, packing, and shipping is performed accurately&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform all activities, utilizing tools and equipment (scales, RF guns, auto-bagger, IT systems) to maximize output&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all bins and work areas/stations are maintained in an orderly, organized, and trash-free manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain inventory accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performs all other duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Quality&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for production accuracy and for providing feedback to management regarding errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable in attendance and punctuality; completes assigned responsibilities to satisfaction; follows through with commitments&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follows rules and code of conduct at work; demonstrates an ethical behavior at work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Customer Value&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communication, ability to balance talking with listening&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster Crescent excellence by cultivating teamwork&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively communicate directly to all aspects of production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a good working relationship with internal customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Financial&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align and optimize the allocation of People to meet established production targets&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balances immediate and long-term priorities: seeks to meet critical objectives while considering the impact of those decisions and activities on the ability to achieve long-term goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
